{"tid":1332381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家小心721既遊行終點","createTime":"2019-07-19T09:36:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T20:57:59.000Z","uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aa00bbe2c6c064318343673aa9ad99ac1d058530","tid":1332381,"uid":278698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:36:05.000Z","msg":"每次遊行，警察都係好有計劃咁夾擊同埋拘捕你<br />\n<br />\n沙田 上水 尖咀，相信大家都有目共睹<br />\n<br />\n今次721遊行終點係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">終審法院</span><br />\n<br />\n我有一個大膽假設，黑警一定無所不用其極，叫d黑底扮發夢人士衝入終審法院，如果真係咁做，黑警今次一定唔會好似立法會果日咁等，取之代之係會入終審圍堵，或者用更升級既暴力<br />\n<br />\n所以我地遊行完，應該要發夢去其他地方升級，咩地方未諗到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但千祈唔好搞終院</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n因為法律界，好多仲係我地既朋友，有馬道立，有黑衣遊行等等等，見到有人搞終院，要捉住同起底同check 下佢地有冇單程證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d80b3d60e4e97530458287a8f413f58e53132f","tid":1332381,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:36:33.000Z","msg":"【有人冒警】面對冒警情境練習場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332100\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332100</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"f51fbf8fccedaecf3a671b78fbbdd780638f0d69","tid":1332381,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:36:39.000Z","msg":"無睇新聞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b77ddbfca29b3f5d67d941b0b038d7e9001a62c","tid":1332381,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:37:56.000Z","msg":"最壞打算 封2隧道<br />\n黑警玩主動圍捕<br />\n有咩做唔出"},{"pid":"7fc5f79477f2497e03cd2133e79f6a367a114cdb","tid":1332381,"uid":267328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f51fbf8fccedaecf3a671b78fbbdd780638f0d69","tid":1332381,"uid":76591,"